(22, '联系我们', '<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"4\" width=\"90%\" bgcolor=\"#d5d5d5\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor=\"#fcfcfc\">\r\n				<div align=\"center\">\r\n					<span>如果您遇到任何问题，请与我们取得联系，我们定会以热情的服务给你满意的答复，感谢您光临本网站！</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\r\n				<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td width=\"120\">\r\n								<div align=\"right\">\r\n									<span>办公地址:</span>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</td>\r\n							<td>\r\n								<span>广西贵港市金港大道XX号</span>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor=\"#fbfbfb\">\r\n				<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td width=\"120\">\r\n								<div align=\"right\">\r\n									<span>工厂地址:</span>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</td>\r\n							<td>\r\n								<span>广西贵港市覃塘XX工业区</span>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\r\n				<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td width=\"120\">\r\n								<div align=\"right\">\r\n									<span>联系电话:</span>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</td>\r\n							<td>\r\n								<span>0775-4000001 　0775-4000002&nbsp;　0775-4000003<br />\r\n</span>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor=\"#fbfbfb\">\r\n				<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td width=\"120\">\r\n								<div align=\"right\">\r\n									<span>传真号码:</span>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</td>\r\n							<td>\r\n								<span>0775-4000000</span>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\r\n				<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td